    "instructions": [
        "Heat the butter in a large pan until foaming, then add the onions, garlic, and shallots. Cook gently for 15-20 minutes until really soft and starting to caramelise. ",
        "Turn up the heat and add the flour. Cook for 2-3 minutes, then stir in the sugar, vinegar and mustard. ",
        "Add the rosemary and stock; simmer briskly for 15 minutes until thickened. Season and keep warm."
